            "/Library/Audio/Presets/Xfer Records/Serum 2 Presets/Presets/S1 Presets/Speed Garage/Bass- Turn Back Time.fxp"
          ],
          "notes": "Use Hyper first to split the 162/163 boundary. Filter On is the explicit fallback if Hyper is too noisy."
        }
      ]
    },
